$ /etc/login.defs

Configuration control definitions for the login/shadow package.

Three defitions are required: `MAIL_DIR`, `ENV_SUPATH` and `ENV_PATH`. The others are optional.

sa:

 `→ Linux/shell/commands/useradd` (especially the `-K` command line option).

 `→ Linux/fhs/etc/pam_d`

 `→ Linux/shell/commands/umask`
